  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BooleanDataField
    Instance of this class represents boolean value.
    ByteDataField
    A class that represents array of bytes field.
    CircularBufferQueue
    CircularBufferQueue is in-memory queue for data records.
    CloverDataRecordSerializer
    DataRecordSerializer that uses internal DataField serialization.
    CompressedByteDataField
    Class implementing field which represents gzip-compressed array of bytes.
    CompressingDataRecordSerializer
    DataRecordSerializer with improved compression of string, list and map data fields.
    DataField
    An interface that represents data field and its value.
    DataFieldFactory
    Factory Pattern which creates different types of DataField objects (subclasses) based on specified data field type.
    DataFieldImpl
    A class that represents data field and its value.
    DataFieldWithInvalidState
    This data field implementation is simple wrapper for a DataField instance.
    DataRecord
    An interface that represents one data record with structure based on provided metadata object.
    DataRecordFactory
    Class for factorisation of DataRecord object.
    DataRecordImpl
    A class that represents one data record with structure based on provided metadata object.
    DataRecordMap
    Specialized hash map implementation for storing DataRecords with the single RecordKey.
    DataRecordWithInvalidState
    Implementation of DataRecord interface, which use DataFieldWithInvalidState instead of regular DataFieldImpl.
    DateDataField
    Represents a date data field.
    DecimalDataField
    A class that represents decimal number field (precision, scale pair)
    Defaults
    Helper class which contains some framework-wide constants definitions.
    Defaults.Component
    Defaults for various components
    Defaults.ConnectionPool
    Defaults for file operations' connection pool.
    Defaults.CTL
    Default settings for CTL.
    Defaults.Data
    Defaults for section Data
    Defaults.Data.StringDataField

    Defaults.DataFormatter

    Defaults.DataParser

    Defaults for port reading/writing - stream mode.
    Defaults.Record
    Defaults regarding DataRecord structure/manipulation
    Defaults.WatchDog  
    DoubleRecordBuffer
    Represents a buffer of two data records that can be swapped.
    DynamicRecordBuffer
    Class implementing DynamicRecordBuffer backed by temporary file - i.e. unlimited size
    Implements FIFO: write & read operations can be interleaved, however it deteriorates performance if data has to be swap to disk (if internal buffer is exhausted).
    ExternalSortDataRecord
    Class for external sorting of data records.
    FileRecordBuffer
    Class implementing RecordBuffer backed by temporary file - i.e. unlimited size
    Implements FIFO: push & shift operations can be interleaved, however it deteriorates performance.
    GetVal
    Supporting "macros" for getting values of differend data fields.
    GraphElementDescriptionImpl
    Ascendant of all plugin elements description like ComponentDescription, SequenceDescription, ConnectionDescription etc.
    HashKey
    Class associated with RecorKey and DataRecord Intended primarily to be used as a key for HashTable It only points to RecordKey and particular data record so we can perform hashing & lookup of the data record.
    IntegerDataField
    A class that represents integer number field (32bit signed)
    InternalSortDataRecord
    Class for simple in-memory sorting of data records.
    ListDataField
    This data field implementation represents a list of fields, which are uniformly typed by a simple type (string, integer, decimal, ...).
    LongDataField
    A class that represents integer number field (32bit signed)
    MapDataField
    This data field implementation represents a map of fields, which are uniformly typed by a simple type (string, integer, decimal, ...).
    NullRecord
    This class represents record will all fields with null value.
    NumericDataField
    A class that represents decimal number field (double precision)
    PersistentBufferQueue
    Regular queue for CloverBuffers backed by temporary files.
    PluginableItemDescriptionImpl
    Parent class for all pluginable item descriptors.
    RecordComapratorAnyOrderType
    Compares two data records with the same structure.
    RecordComparator
    This class compares two records of the same structure (created based on the same or at least compatible metadata).
    RecordKey
    This class serves the role of DataRecords comparator.
    RecordOrderedComparator  
    RecordOrderedKey
    This class serves the role of DataRecords comparator.
    RingRecordBuffer
    This record buffer implement FIFO record storage with limited number of records.
    SetVal
    Supporting "macros" for setting values of differend data fields
    StringDataField
    A class that represents String type data field.
    Token
    Token is simple extension of DataRecord, which is used in jobflow run of a graph.
